                                    "patching_rect": [ 2634.848252415657, 518.1817724704742, 202.13903152942657, 23.0 ],
                                    "text": "oUTPUT 8 - Pressure Trigger"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "fontname": "LEMON MILK",
                                    "fontsize": 12.0,
                                    "id": "obj-125",
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3033.3330657482147, 625.7575205564499, 194.6524007320404, 23.0 ],
                                    "text": "MIDI Clock",
                                    "textjustification": 1
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "fontname": "LEMON MILK",
                                    "fontsize": 12.0,
                                    "id": "obj-124",
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3033.3330657482147, 851.5150763988495, 194.6524007320404, 23.0 ],
                                    "text": "oUTPUT 25 - MIDI Reset"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "fontname": "LEMON MILK",
                                    "fontsize": 12.0,
                                    "id": "obj-123",
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3033.3330657482147, 825.757502913475, 194.6524007320404, 23.0 ],
                                    "text": "oUTPUT 24 - Active Sensing"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-76",
                                    "linecount": 10,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3233.33304810524, 775.7575073242188, 157.0, 144.0 ],
                                    "text": "Reset is a MIDI system reset. Here it is a single-sample impulse of 1. \n\nActive sensing is broadcast periodically by some midi devices to notify that the device is still connected. Here it is a single-sample impulse of 1. "
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-83",
                                    "linecount": 19,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3233.33304810524, 340.9090608358383, 155.0, 269.0 ],
                                    "text": "Sysex\n\nTrig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new sysex event happens.\n\nGate == 1 from the first sysex data byte output through to the last. When gate drops back to zero, the sysex dump is complete. \n\nCount is the number of sysex bytes transferred so far.\n\nByte is the actual sysex byte values (integer)"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-84",
                                    "linecount": 5,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3231.8178967237473, 253.03028070926666, 155.0, 75.0 ],
                                    "text": "Channel\n\nThe MIDI channel value, updated for all of the event types to the left. "
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-85",
                                    "linecount": 9,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3231.8178967237473, 112.12120223045349, 155.0, 131.0 ],
                                    "text": "Program Change\n\nTrig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new program change event happens. \n\nProgram is the program change value (integer)"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-88",
                                    "linecount": 9,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 2843.939143061638, 739.393874168396, 155.0, 131.0 ],
                                    "text": "Pitch bend\n\nTrig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new bend event happens. \n\nBend is the pitch bend amount, normalized in -1..1. "
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "id": "obj-89",
                                    "linecount": 17,
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 2843.939143061638, 486.36359345912933, 155.0, 241.0 ],
                                    "text": "Pressure (aftertouch). \n\nTrig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new pressure event happens. \n\nPressure is the intensity normalized to a 0..1 range.\n\nPressureIsNote == 1 if the  event is a poly pressure (per note) event, or 0 if it was a channel pressure. \n\nPressurePitch is the midinote value for poly pressure events (integer)"
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
                                    "fontname": "LEMON MILK",
                                    "fontsize": 12.0,
                                    "id": "obj-82",
                                    "maxclass": "comment",
                                    "numinlets": 1,
                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 2643.9391607046127, 328.7878497838974, 194.6524007320404, 23.0 ],
                                    "text": "Continuous controller",
                                    "textjustification": 1
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
