                                    "numoutlets": 0,
                                    "patching_rect": [ 3233.33304810524, 625.7575205564499, 155.0, 144.0 ],
                                    "text": "Active == 1 while the clock is playing. Active == 0 when stopped/paused. \n\nTick is nonzero for 1 sample every 24ppqn. \n\nCount is the number of ticks since the transport was started/rewound. "
                                }
                            },
