                                    "patching_rect": [ 2845.4542944431305, 328.7878497838974, 148.0, 144.0 ],
                                    "text": "Trig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new CC event happens. \n\nCCnum is the CC parameter (integer)\n\nCCval is the CC value normalized to a 0..1 range."
                                }
                            },
                            {
                                "box": {
