                                    "text": "Trig is nonzero for 1 sample when a new note event happens. \n\nGate == 1 if the event is noteon. Handles noteon with velocity=0 as a noteoff. \n\nPitch is MIDI note value (integer). \n\nVelocity is normalized to 0..1 range."
